    overview: `• Public photonics, compound semiconductors, and laser technology company (NYSE: COHR)\n• Formed through II-VI acquiring Coherent in Jul 2022 for $7.2B and taking the Coherent name\n• Headquartered in Saxonburg, PA\n• CEO Mark Sobey\n• ~28,000+ employees globally\n• Revenue ~$5.2B (FY2025)\n• Products span optical communications (data center transceivers), semiconductor equipment (SiC substrates for EVs), laser materials processing, and aerospace/defense\n• AI data center boom drives massive demand for 800G/1.6T optical transceivers`,
